@666  = ~(Bring the gauntleted hand into line with the rest of the symbols.)~
@667  = ~(Bring the mask into line with the rest of the symbols.) ~
@668  = ~(Bring the jeweled sunrise into line with the rest of the symbols.)~
@669  = ~(Put the box away.)~
@670  = ~(You recognize the symbols as the holy symbols of Faerunian deities. The symbols engraved on the box correspond with Bane, Auril, and Shar. Those on the movable band correspond with Tyr, Torm, Mask, and Lathander. You...)~
